## Decision Template

When adding a new decision:

```markdown
| # | YYYY-MM-DD | [What was decided] | [Option A, Option B, Option C] | [Why this option was chosen — include data/metrics if available] |
```

For complex decisions, add a detailed section below the table:

```markdown
### Decision #N: [Title]
**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD
**Context:** What prompted this decision
**Options:**
1. **[Option A]** — Pros: ... / Cons: ...
2. **[Option B]** — Pros: ... / Cons: ...
3. **[Option C]** — Pros: ... / Cons: ...
**Decision:** Option B
**Reasoning:** [Detailed reasoning]
**Consequences:** [What this means for the project]
```

